Primary Question:}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\nowidctlpar\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\cf1\kerning1\dbch\af8\langfe2052\dbch\af13\afs24\alang1081\loch\f5\fs24\lang1033\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0{\cf1\dbch\af10\rtlch \ltrch\loch\loch\f4
Is it possible to build a software framework using existing motion detection hardware in order to create effective, inexpensive, portable, easy to use interactive spaces?}
